{"tid":1133630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）情侶感情糾紛 女方遭男方開車輾過","createTime":"2019-05-01T08:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T01:38:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ce194dbf5d64e9b1433dcb3ae5cf63ee5f7b69","tid":1133630,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/5-1/p2415411a930172265-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F5-1%2Fp2415411a930172265-ss.jpg&h=633e7eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《LTN》綜合外媒報導，4月25日在浙江理工大學校園內某處停車場，有1名紅衣女子坐在地上跟車內的男友發生爭執。<br />\n<br />\n從該影片中可以看到，這名女子緊緊地拉住車門，疑似是要阻止男子離開。但是男子硬是將她踹倒在地，也不顧女方的手仍然抓在車上，就直接向後倒車，導致女子被拖行後趴倒在地。<br />\n<br />\n而男子所開的保時捷轎車更因此直接輾過女子的左腿與左手，引發一旁路人尖叫、報警。在男子輾過女友之後，竟然直接掩上車門，加速逃逸。<br />\n<br />\n這起事件已造成女子左腳1處骨折、全身多處的挫傷，幸好送醫治療後沒有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n據警方表示，該女子是校內學生，但男子卻是校外人士。案發後男子已經被逮捕了，初步了解2人是因為情感糾紛發生爭執，詳細原因還有待釐清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/05/01/892269.html?code=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F05%2F01%2F892269.html%3Fcode%3Db5&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=0d03ac70\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/05/01/892269.html?code=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Ap1RFGHILvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAp1RFGHILvU&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=c73f6957\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=Ap1RFGHILvU</a>"},{"pid":"81d34040262f2728c31abfda520cd794f9194e65","tid":1133630,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:16:10.000Z","msg":"支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f39924fe75ded5f3138e8a1ad6ac7ff5c415dd1","tid":1133630,"uid":1915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy